{"thag1.8:0.1":"Theragatha 1.8 ","thag1.8:0.2":"Ekakanipata ","thag1.8:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag1.8:0.4":"Virattheragatha ","thag1.8:1.1":"“Yo duddamiyo damena danto, ","thag1.8:1.2":"Viro santusito vitinnakankho; ","thag1.8:1.3":"Vijitavi apetalomahamso, ","thag1.8:1.4":"Viro so parinibbuto thitatto”ti. ","thag1.8:1.5":"Ittham sudam ayasma viro thero gatham abhasitthati. "}